                <p>The first step is a private conversation. You can <a href="/book">book a consultation</a> to explain your needs and ask questions before reviewing candidates. We will discuss the number and ages of your children, your preferred schedule, whether you need live-in or live-out support, and any priorities around experience, language, travel, or household duties.</p>
                <p>After consultation, we can guide you toward suitable options and, where appropriate, share a private shortlist. You may also <a href="/candidates">view candidate examples</a> to understand the type of profiles families may review after consultation. If you are still exploring the wider service, you can return to the <a href="/">Trusted Household &amp; Childcare homepage</a> for an overview of our household staffing approach.</p>
